Name: Send a new touch of fire in my soul Lord
ChorusText:
Send a new touch of fire in my soul Lord
Send it now Lord, send it now,
Touch my lips
today
with a burning coal,
Send a new touch of fire in my soul
Send a new touch of fire in my soul Lord
Send it now Lord, send it now,
Touch my lips
tonight
with a burning coal,
Send a new touch of fire in my soul
